                      00027     
                      00028 ;****************************************************************************************
                      00029 ;****                        CURRENT_DRIVE_STATE Bit Map                              ***
                      00030 ;****************************************************************************************
                      00031 ;****  Current Drive State is Set up so that the lower Nibble(Bits 0-3) indicate the  ***
                      00032 ;***    right motor Function and the upper nibble(Bits 4-7) indicate the left motor   ***
                      00033 ;***    function.  Looking at the nibbles individually, a decimal 0=Stop, 1=Forward,  ***
                      00034 ;***    and 2=Reverse.                                                                ***
                      00035 ;****************************************************************************************
                      00036 ;***_________________________________________________________________________________ ***
                      00037 ;***| Hex Value  |      Mode Name         |            Motor Function               | ***
                      00038 ;***|    0x00    |      All Stop          | Right Motor Stop, Left Motor Stop       | ***
                      00039 ;***|    0x11    |    Drive Forward       | Right Motor Forward, Left Motor Forward | ***
                      00040 ;***|    0x22    |    Drive Reverse       | Right Motor Reverse, Left Motor Reverse | ***       
                      00041 ;***|    0x10    |  Turn Right Forward    | Right Motor Stop, Left Motor Forward    | ***    
                      00042 ;***|    0x02    |  Turn Right Reverse    | Right Motor Reverse, Left Motor Stop    | ***
                      00043 ;***|    0x12    | Zero-Point Turn Right  | Right Motor Reverse, Left Motor Forward | ***    
                      00044 ;***|    0x01    |  Turn Left Forward     | Right Motor Forward, Left Motor Stop    | ***    
                      00045 ;***|    0x20    |  Turn Left Reverse     | Right Motor Stop, Left Motor Reverse    | ***
                      00046 ;***|    0x21    | Zero-Point Turn Left   | Right Motor Forward, Left Motor Reverse | ***
                      00047 ;***|    0x__    | Unrecognized; All Stop | Right Motor Stop, Left Motor Stop       | ***
                      00048 ;***_________________________________________________________________________________ ***
                      00049 ;****************************************************************************************
                      00050     
